        %p.label-55{:style => "margin-bottom:5px;"}
          Collaborate:
          %span.label-56 Collaborate with other enthusiasts
        %p.label-55{:style => "margin-bottom: 5px;"}
          Be Active:
          %span.label-56
            You have a user group in your city. Stay active on it, participate and contribute regularly. The more you meet-up, the more you learn and have fun.

        %p.label-55{:style => "margin-bottom: 5px;"}
